{
  "texts": [
    "As previously mentioned, different regions have different Auslan expressions.",
    "Our system compares the similarity of high-dimensional features between the user-inputted Auslan video and our demonstration videos in the Auslan recognition network.",
    "This allows us to provide demonstrations that best match user needs, accommodating regional variations in Auslan.",
    "User evaluationIn order to obtain authentic user evaluations, we develop a new family engaged evaluation methodology, which is specifically designed to measure our IACH's impact on family communication.",
    "We select ten families in the surrounding area, consisting of parents and children."
  ]
}